{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"vwa.la help","description":"Everything you need to know about the vwa.la influencer marketing platform."}},"ghostPost":{"title":"Buffer","slug":"buffer","featured":false,"feature_image":"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/09/buffer.png","created_at_pretty":"20 September, 2018","published_at_pretty":"20 September, 2018","updated_at_pretty":"19 November, 2018","created_at":"2018-09-20T18:07:05.000+00:00","published_at":"2018-09-20T18:07:16.000+00:00","updated_at":"2018-11-19T10:34:39.000+00:00","excerpt":"Post to all your social accounts automatically every time a new post is\npublished with Ghost, thanks to Buffer\n\nThe main benefit to using Buffer with Ghost is to automate and schedule your\npublication's social strategy with minimal overhead. Rather than manually\nremembering to share a new post in all the right places, do it in bulk using\nBuffer to share at the best times for your audience.\n\nShare new posts from Ghost to Buffer\nThe easiest way to set up automatic sharing is by using the official\n","meta_title":null,"meta_description":"Keep your social accounts in sync with your Ghost content using Buffer! Find out how to integrate your content & automate social sharing ðŸ“£","og_description":null,"og_image":null,"og_title":null,"twitter_description":null,"twitter_image":null,"twitter_title":null,"authors":[{"name":"John O'Nolan","slug":"john","bio":null,"profile_image":"//www.gravatar.com/avatar/f95828f4e92f1befebabfb7f65cdc8f2?s=250&d=mm&r=x","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":null}],"primary_author":{"name":"John O'Nolan","slug":"john","bio":null,"profile_image":"//www.gravatar.com/avatar/f95828f4e92f1befebabfb7f65cdc8f2?s=250&d=mm&r=x","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":null},"primary_tag":{"name":"Automation","slug":"automation","description":null,"feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},"tags":[{"name":"Automation","slug":"automation","description":null,"feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},{"name":"Social","slug":"social","description":null,"feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},{"name":"#integration","slug":"hash-integration","description":null,"feature_image":null,"meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"internal"}],"plaintext":"Post to all your social accounts automatically every time a new post is\npublished with Ghost, thanks to Buffer\n\nThe main benefit to using Buffer with Ghost is to automate and schedule your\npublication's social strategy with minimal overhead. Rather than manually\nremembering to share a new post in all the right places, do it in bulk using\nBuffer to share at the best times for your audience.\n\nShare new posts from Ghost to Buffer\nThe easiest way to set up automatic sharing is by using the official\nGhost<>Zapier integration which will allow you to deliver new Ghost posts\ndirectly into your Buffer account.\n\nFrom there, you can decide exactly how and when you'd like your individual\nstatuses to be scheduled for sharing.\n\nMore automation with Zapier\nYou can also go further and connect other popular Ghost integrations with Buffer\nusing Zapier, so you can build out complimentary workflows for the rest of your\npublication.","html":"<p>Post to all your social accounts automatically every time a new post is published with Ghost, thanks to Buffer</p><p>The main benefit to using Buffer with Ghost is to automate and schedule your publication's social strategy with minimal overhead. Rather than manually remembering to share a new post in all the right places, do it in bulk using Buffer to share at the best times for your audience.</p><h2 id=\"share-new-posts-from-ghost-to-buffer\">Share new posts from Ghost to Buffer</h2><p>The easiest way to set up automatic sharing is by using the official Ghost&lt;&gt;Zapier integration which will allow you to deliver new Ghost posts directly into your Buffer account.</p><p>From there, you can decide exactly how and when you'd like your individual statuses to be scheduled for sharing.</p><div id=\"zap\" class=\"zapier\">\n    <script src=\"https://zapier.com/apps/embed/widget.js?services=buffer,ghost&limit=2&html_id=zap\"></script>\n</div><h2 id=\"more-automation-with-zapier\">More automation with Zapier</h2><p>You can also go further and connect other popular Ghost integrations with Buffer using Zapier, so you can build out complimentary workflows for the rest of your publication.</p><div id=\"zap2\" class=\"zapier\">\n    <script src=\"https://zapier.com/apps/embed/widget.js?services=buffer&limit=2&html_id=zap2\"></script>\n</div>","custom_template":null,"url":"https://docs.ghost.io/buffer/","uuid":"0d190350-1601-4b83-8083-ed8f555717ec","page":false,"codeinjection_foot":"","codeinjection_head":"","comment_id":"5ba3e1c906626b00bf606645"},"file":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":30,"height":30,"src":"/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/2682d/integration-icon.png","srcSet":"/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/2682d/integration-icon.png 1x,\n/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/0b300/integration-icon.png 1.5x,\n/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/5d50f/integration-icon.png 2x,\n/static/f999857e2481e5281e1dc0eec5a292d7/95621/integration-icon.png 3x"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"buffer","relatedPosts":[{"node":{"slug":"custom-integrations","title":"Custom","url":"/integrations/custom-integrations/","published_at":"2018-11-11T09:07:55.000+00:00","feature_image":"https://docs.ghost.io/content/images/2018/11/custom.svg","tags":[{"slug":"utility","name":"Utility","description":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null},{"slug":"automation","name":"Automation","description":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"feature_image":null},{"slug":"content","name":"Content","description":nu